## 3. Replace `/var/www/cortexbuild-ultimate/src/context/AuthContext.tsx`
Replace Supabase auth with local JWT auth. The context should:
- On mount: check `getToken()` + `getStoredUser()`, set `isAuthenticated` and `user`
- `login(email, password)`: POST to `/api/auth/login`, store token and user on success
- `logout()`: call `clearToken()`, set isAuthenticated to false
- Export: `user`, `isAuthenticated`, `loading`, `login`, `logout`

The login function signature should match what `LoginPage.tsx` expects. Look at the existing LoginPage to understand the interface.

Make sure to import from `../lib/supabase` (which now exports getToken, setToken, clearToken, getStoredUser, setStoredUser, API_BASE).

